The paper introduces a new graph class called pairwise compatibility graphs (PCG) and provides necessary and sufficient conditions for PCG based on cut-vertices and twins. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Graph Theory (cs.GT), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
